ement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableElement\"><code>HTMLTableElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableRowElement\"><code>HTMLTableRowElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTableSectionElement\"><code>HTMLTableSectionElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTemplateElement\"><code>HTMLTemplateElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTextAreaElement\"><code>HTMLTextAreaElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTimeElement\"><code>HTMLTimeElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTitleElement\"><code>HTMLTitleElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLTrackElement\"><code>HTMLTrackElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUListElement\"><code>HTMLUListElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLUnknownElement\"><code>HTMLUnknownElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLVideoElement\"><code>HTMLVideoElement</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HashChangeEvent\"><code>HashChangeEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/History\"><code>History</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ImageData\"><code>ImageData</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Location\"><code>Location</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageEvent\"><code>MessageEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Navigator\"><code>Navigator</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PageTransitionEvent\"><code>PageTransitionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Plugin\"><code>Plugin</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PluginArray\"><code>PluginArray</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PopStateEvent\"><code>PopStateEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/PromiseRejectionEvent\"><code>PromiseRejectionEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/RadioNodeList\"><code>RadioNodeList</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/ValidityState\"><code>ValidityState</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Window\"><code>Window</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>A&nbsp;interface&nbsp;<strong><code>MessageChannel</code></strong> da&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Channel_Messaging_API\">API Channel Messaging</a>&nbsp;nos permite criar um&nbsp;novo canal de mensagem e enviar os dados através&nbsp;de suas duas propriedades&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a>.</p>\n\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect1\">\n  <p><strong>Note:</strong> This feature is available in <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Web_Workers_API\">Web Workers</a></p>\n</div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propriedades","title":"Propriedades","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"messagechannel.port1_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel/port1\"><code>MessageChannel.port1</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></dt>\n <dd>Retorna port1 do&nbsp;canal.</dd>\n <dt id=\"messagechannel.port2_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel/port2\"><code>MessageChannel.port2</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></dt>\n <dd>Retorna&nbsp;port2 do&nbsp;canal.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"construtor","title":"Construtor","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"messagechannel_en-us\"><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel/MessageChannel\"><code>MessageChannel()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></dt>\n <dd>\n <p>Retorna um&nbsp;novo&nbsp;objeto&nbsp;<code>MessageChannel</code> com dois&nbsp;novos&nbsp;objetos&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MessagePort\"><code>MessagePort</code></a>.</p>\n </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplo","title":"Exemplo","isH3":false,"content":"<p>No seguinte bloco de codigo, você pode ver um novo canal sendo criado usando o construtor&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel/MessageChannel\"><code>MessageChannel()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>. Quando o&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/iframe\"><code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code></a> tiver carregado, nos passamos&nbsp;o <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessageChannel/port2\"><code>MessageChannel.port2</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> para o <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/iframe\"><code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code></a> usando <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/MessagePort/postMessage\"><code>MessagePort.postMessage</code></a> juntamente com uma mensagem. O manipulador&nbsp;<code>handleMessage</code>&nbsp;então reponde&nbsp;à mensagem que foi enviada de volta do&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/HTML/Element/iframe\"><code>&lt;iframe&gt;</code></a> (using <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MessagePort/message_event\"><code>MessagePort.onmessage</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>), colocando-o em um parágrafo.</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> channel <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">MessageChannel</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> para <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'p'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> ifr <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'iframe'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> otherWindow <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> ifr<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>contentWindow<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nifr<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"load\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> iframeLoaded<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">false</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">iframeLoaded</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  otherWindow<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">postMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Hello from the main page!'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">'*'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>channel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>port2<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\nchannel<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>port1<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>onmessage <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> handleMessage<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">handleMessage</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">e</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  para<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>innerHTML <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> e<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>data<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>   </code></pre></div>\n\n<p>Para um exemplo completo, veja nosso&nbsp; <a class=\"external external-icon\" href=\"https://github.com/mdn/dom-examples/tree/master/channel-messaging-basic\" rel=\" noopener\">channel messaging basic demo</a>&nbsp;no Github (<a class=\"external external-icon\" href=\"https://mdn.github.io/dom-examples/channel-messaging-basic/\" rel=\" noopener\">rode&nbsp;online também</a>&nbsp;).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificações</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/web-messaging.html#message-channels\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Message channels' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>&